戰力膨脹到痴線<br />\n勁撚多bug<br />\n最尾佐助回心轉意得不知所謂 明明佢除左手法極端之外 思想係完冇問題<br />\n但唔知點解鳴人係佢朋友=我錯了要贖罪<br />\non9到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n火影呢套垃圾真係見到都想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢套乜柒博人傳<br />\n見到博人呢條柒頭就會諗起鳴人同大波田係幾咁on9 火影係幾咁垃圾<br />\n<br />\non9先會睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：前忠實fan屎"},{"pid":"813cdfaf2f62fce0287b6fd753f3b0301e2cf337","tid":361201,"uid":4402,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T22:43:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n結局本身已經垃圾<br />\n為左繼續賺錢而湊幾對九唔搭八既情侶去生仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n畫撚死寧次又唔知係做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佐助唔知點解又鍾意左港女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鳴人講左十幾年話鍾意港女最尾靠套垃圾劇場版個90分鐘推翻曬<br />\n<br />\n唔係話唔比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一早想咁畫咪早d安排好 做乜要畫到咁難睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n忍界大戰又唔知做乜鳩 佐鳴變左輪回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要戰力膨脹到痴線<br />\n勁撚多bug<br />\n最尾佐助回心轉意得不知所謂 明明佢除左手法極端之外 思想係完冇問題<br />\n但唔知點解鳴人係佢朋友=我錯了要贖罪<br />\non9到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n火影呢套垃圾真係見到都想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢套乜柒博人傳<br />\n見到博人呢條柒頭就會諗起鳴人同大波田係幾咁on9 火影係幾咁垃圾<br />\n<br />\non9先會睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：前忠實fan屎</blockquote><br />\n岸本好似講過 雛田條線係佩恩篇已經定左係鳴仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鹿丸條線 中忍考試開始已經係人都明啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係井野同港女櫻條線比較勉強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佐助個性格真係寧願比鳴仔屌屎眼都唔會鐘意港女櫻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9412df66d5477693ab11ac5591b79b0b4473a92","tid":361201,"uid":96704,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T01:37:17.000Z","msg":"依家做到佐助個女搵老豆<br />\n佐助由細到大都要俾人搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71a51e1867c39276c0ca1113701f298e5d36f700","tid":361201,"uid":19012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T01:47:21.000Z","msg":"就好似睇緊龍珠 （悟飯擔正）一模一樣<br />\n<br />\n一開始就打外星人"}]}